components.name: Geocode Facilities Using HERE API
components.description: Geocodes facility addresses via the HERE API, adding latitude and longitude columns. Uses image default entrypoint.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful load and modify step

components.name: Calculate Distance to Nearest Public Transport
components.description: Computes distance from each facility to the nearest public transport stop/hub and adds a distance_to_pt column. Uses image default entrypoint.

components.name: Calculate Distance to Nearest Residential Area
components.description: Computes distance from each facility to the nearest residential area and adds a distance_to_residential column. Uses image default entrypoint.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after distance to public transport calculation
